      "message": "Line 42: reset() leaves lastPeriodicLog_ unchanged. After a sender restart or session restart, the controller state is reset but status logging may be suppressed until the previous 5-second cadence expires, making restart behavior harder to diagnose. Reset all timing state consistently.\n```suggestion\n    lastPeriodicLog_ \u003d time_point::min();\n```",
